<!-- THE CHALLENGE -->
<p class="section-label">/ The Challenge</p>
<h2 class="h2" style="max-width:660px;margin-bottom:32px;">A blank sheet. One goal. An industry to disrupt.</h2>
<p class="body-lg" style="max-width:896px;margin-bottom:48px;">Bia Energy came to us with no brand, no identity, and no public presence. Entering a competitive clean energy market, they had a powerful story but no visual language to tell it. The challenge was precise: craft an identity that balanced trust and innovation without tipping into corporate blankness or greenwashing. The brand had to work in a hi-vis jacket, on a conference stage, and in a B2B sales conversation — simultaneously.</p>

