<!-- THE SOLUTION -->
<p class="section-label">/ The Solution</p>
<h2 class="h2" style="max-width:660px;margin-bottom:32px;">Strategy before design. Every time.</h2>
<p class="body-lg" style="max-width:896px;margin-bottom:48px;">We opened with user persona research and a semi-fictional archetype model to map Bia Energy's B2B audience — demographics, psychographics, behaviours. This fed a full client discovery workshop covering voice, values, and positioning. Identity work began only once the strategic foundation was set.</p>

