<!-- WHAT WE DELIVERED -->
<p class="section-label">/ What we delivered</p>
<h2 class="h2" style="max-width:660px;margin-bottom:32px;">Everything. From first brief to launch day.</h2>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px;margin-bottom:48px;align-items:start;">
  <div>
    <p class="body-lg" style="margin-bottom:32px;">This was an end-to-end engagement — one of those rare projects where we touched every layer of the brand's public presence.</p>
    <ul class="cs-deliverables">
      <li>Brand Identity &amp; Guidelines</li>
      <li>Content Creation</li>
      <li>Marketing Collateral</li>
      <li>Custom WordPress Build</li>
      <li>Carbon Calculator</li>
      <li>Launch Event</li>
      <li>AV &amp; Photography</li>
      <li>Conference Materials</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p class="body-base">The website required a bespoke WordPress theme — purpose-built, not templated — alongside a custom carbon offset calculator allowing B2B clients to model their own savings. The launch event brought the brand to market with a fully coordinated keynote, mailing campaign, and AV production.</p>
  </div>
</div>

